com.opengamma.strata.basics.market

Interface TypedReferenceData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImmutableTypedReferenceData

    public interface TypedReferenceData
    Provides typed access to reference data, such as securities and time-series.

    Reference data is looked up in ReferenceData using implementations of ReferenceDataId. The result is an instance of this interface that allows multiple pieces of reference data to be associated with the same identifier, based on the data type.

    The standard implementation is ImmutableTypedReferenceData.
